    <div class="flickrentry entry">
        <h4>Ten Years in My Life: My Love Life</h4>

        <a href="http://flickr.com/photos/groovymother/2968947740/"><img class="flickrphoto" alt="Ten Years in My Life: My Love Life" src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3187/2968947740_714496a6df_m.jpg" height="240" width="237" /></a>

        <p>
            <p>On Saturday, 24th October 1998, I flew from Glasgow to Boston, with little more than a suitcase of clothes and a credit card with a decently high limit.</p>

<p>It's now 24th October 2008.  Ten years have gone by.  Time for little personal retrospection.  How have I spent these ten years?</p>
        </p>

