<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    <div class="flickrentry entry">
        <h4>My first appearance on Current TV</h4>

        <a href="http://flickr.com/photos/groovymother/2384533152/"><img class="flickrphoto" alt="My first appearance on Current TV" src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2252/2384533152_e5d76580c3_m.jpg" height="180" width="240" /></a>

        <p>
            <p>Or, more accurately, my <i>avatar</i>'s first appearance on Current.</p>

<p>A <a href="http://current.com/items/88882788_#88884867">comment</a> I posted to the website was pulled into the <a href="http://current.com/items/88885078_current_news">Current News broadcast at 11pm<a>.</p>

<p>More details of what's going on at <a href="http://www.techcrunch.com/2008/04/02/current-news-an-even-easier-way-for-web-audiences-to-get-on-tv/">TechCrunch</a>.</a></a></p>
        </p>

