        <h4>My favourite wedding photo</h4>

        <a href="http://flickr.com/photos/groovymother/2332036646/"><img class="flickrphoto" alt="My favourite wedding photo" src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3260/2332036646_5e5c0110f3_m.jpg" height="158" width="240" /></a>

